&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You combine rigorous analytics, strong product sense, and clear communication to drive decisive action in a fast-paced environment. You enjoy rolling up your sleeves, collaborating across disciplines, and using experimentation to uncover what truly helps customers find the right items quickly.&lt;/p&gt;
